## Waterfall Planning Workflow

- [ ] 1. Define project scope and phases
- [ ] 2. Break down work within each phase
- [ ] 3. Define phase dependencies and gates
- [ ] 4. Create detailed phase schedules
- [ ] 5. Establish phase entry/exit criteria
- [ ] 6. Monitor and manage phase transitions

